      "title": "Importing 10 essential items through open accounts allowed from July",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Permission has been granted to import 10 essential items including rice, sugar, wheat flour and dhal through open accounts, the Minister of Trade says.",
        "Thereby, import of these 10 essential items will be permitted from the 01st of July."
      ],
